 
############ Follow these Instructions to make the ETL process automatic ########

1. start hdfs   -> start-dfs.sh
2. start yarn   -> start-yarn.sh
3. start spark  -> start-master.sh
4. start worker -> start-worker.sh spark://ubuntu:7077


5. From "Miniproject" folder copy "miniproject.hql" file into $HIVE_HOME/  -> cp miniproject.hql $HIVE_HOME/
6. Start hive and create database and table according to "hiveQuery.hql" file or follow commands as used in "hiveoutput.txt" file
7. Make a crontab according "cronjob.txt" file
8. Done

